      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Esaijus: Schi buhs ta Sihme no ta KUNGA/ ka tas KUNGS scho Leetu dar-rihs/ ko wiꞥſch irr runnajs. Buhs tai Ehnai deſmits Zellinus us preekſchu ect/ jeb deſmits Zelli-nus atpakkat?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Iskijus: Tas irr lehti/ ka ta Ehma deſmits Zel-linus us preekſchu ect/ to es ne gribbu/ bet lai ta Ehma deſmits Zellinus atpakkat eet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Praweets Esaijus peetauze to KUNGU/ un tas lik-fe to Ehnu deſmits Zellinus at-pakkat eet/ zaur teem püscheem Zellixeem/ ka tu us preekſchu btja gabijusi pee Akasa Saules Stundeni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tami Laika fuhtija Bro-daks Baledaus/Baledana Dehis tas Babeles Rehninſch/Grahma-tas un Dahwanas us Istju/ jo tas bij dsirdejs/ ka Istijus bija neweffels bijts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Istijus klaustija tohs/ un rabdija teem wiſſu favu Mantas Namnu/ to Sudrabu nn Seltn/un tahs dahrgas Sah-les/ un to labbatu Etji/un wiſſu favu Bruxan-Nainu/ un wiſſ/ kas eekſch winna Mantahm at-rasts kua/ ne kahda Leeta bija wiſſa Namnā nedswiſſā win-na Walstibā/ ko Istijus teem ne buhtu rahdijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nahze tas Praweets Esaijus pee ta Rehnina Istju/ un fazzija us to: Ko irr ſchee Wihrifazzijſchi? un no kurrenes\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "irr tee pee tew nahktichi? tad faz-zija Iskijus: Tee irr no tahhas Semmes atnahktuchi/ no Ba-beles.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas fazzija: Ko irr tee tawā Namnā redſejtchi? un Istijus fazzija: Tee irr wiſſu/ tas mannā Namnā irr/ redſej-tchi/ ne kahda Leeta irr eekſch mannahm Mantahm/ ko esteem ne buhtu rahdijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Esaijus us Istju: Klansi ta KUNGA Wahrdü.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rangi/tas Laiks nahfs/ ka wiſſ/ kas tawā Namnā irr/ un ko tawi Tehwi lihdsfchodeen irr peelikkuſchi/ taps us Babelt wests/ ne neeka taps atlizzinahts/ tafka tas KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir no taweem Behr-neein/ kas no tewis dsins/ ko tu dsemidinas/ taps nemti/ka tee par Kambar-Junkureem buhs ta Babeles Rehnina Ptli.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Istijus fazzija us Esaiju: Ta KUNGA Wahrs irr labs/ ko wiſsch irr runnajs. Wehl fazzija wiſsch: Un ka ne? kad tikcai Meers un Teestba man-nā Laika buhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kas weht no Istijus Leetahm atleek/ un wiſſ wianna Spehks/ un ko wiſsch irr darrijs/ tas Dihkis/ un tas Uhdens Grahwis/ ka tas irr Uhdent Pilfsahta waddinajs/ tas wiſſ irr rakſchts to Rehmnu no Juh-da Laiku-Grahmata.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Istijus aistigge ar Ceccc 3\n"
    }
  ],
